{"tid":717768,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［認真討論］究竟「超市」同「手機」係咪蝗語？","createTime":"2018-06-26T09:38:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-02T04:06:45.000Z","uid":12432,"like":75,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"2a7808d49f2559fc1eb85f442600e5f752c614c7","tid":717768,"uid":12432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T09:38:03.000Z","msg":"頭盔：小弟讀中文出身，但主力唔係研究粵語同語言學，所以只係想拋磚引玉，引起討論。<br />\n<br />\n事緣：<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/717208/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/717208/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n我發覺連登好多人討論粵語／蝗語嗰陣，都係憑印象去判斷，好少拎出論據深入咁討論。<br />\n<br />\n一、首先要定義下咩叫「蝗語」。就我個人嘅理解，「蝗語」係指入侵咗香港本土嘅中國大陸用語。<br />\n二、點樣判斷一個用語係咪「蝗語」？可以睇下個用語出現嘅時間，如果香港早過大陸開始用，咁好大機會唔係「蝗語」。語料可以取自舊報紙、電視、電影，因為我淨係睇到舊報紙，所以下面只可以用舊報紙做例子。<br />\n<br />\n以下係我透過香港舊報紙資料庫（範圍只限1991年前嘅《華僑日報》、《工商日報》、《大公報》）、人民日報圖文數據庫檢索「超市」／「超級市場」、「手機」／「手提電話」所得到嘅一啲發現。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">第一部分：「超市」／「超級市場」</span><br />\n<br />\n（1）「超級市場」喺香港舊報紙出現，最早可見於1960年。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/26/155229_41e24aa5ccee32120a59ecd7c3998cd6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F26%2F155229_41e24aa5ccee32120a59ecd7c3998cd6.jpg&h=18096294&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖一：華僑日報，1960年4月27日。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/26/155331_4f76a82b8ba00c3fcba0541b18623e0c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F26%2F155331_4f76a82b8ba00c3fcba0541b18623e0c.jpg&h=0039cef2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖二：工商日報，1960年11月18日。<br />\n<br />\n（2）「超市」喺香港舊報紙出現，最早可見於1982年，但直至1991年所見，「超市」只會出現喺報導嘅標題，內文會用返「超級市場」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/26/155953_221ea2b0d72eb5b35c9d19092baa9575.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F26%2F155953_221ea2b0d72eb5b35c9d19092baa9575.jpg&h=49e92670&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖三：華僑日報，1982年7月8日。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/26/160136_28e0511814b06eb59b9c51bb0d51f656.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F26%2F160136_28e0511814b06eb59b9c51bb0d51f656.jpg&h=d5d02f97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖四：大公報，1983年7月16日。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/26/161214_71cd37abc40f60b1d4a94032fb103821.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F26%2F161214_71cd37abc40f60b1d4a94032fb103821.jpg&h=6d3c370d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖五：大公報，1989年11月24日。<br />\n<br />\n（3）「超市」喺《人民日報》出現，最早可見於1985年，而且位置不限標題，亦見內文。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/26/160426_6d6cfd25c8cc8e2aca9b5c778882cf7a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F26%2F160426_6d6cfd25c8cc8e2aca9b5c778882cf7a.jpg&h=db9b1816&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖六：人民日報：1985年7月1日第3版。<br />\n<br />\n小結：香港舊報紙用「超市」一詞，時間上早過中國第一大報《人民日報》，但用處只限於標題，內文依然會用返「超級市場」，即使係紅底嘅《大公報》都係咁，可見「超市」應該係香港報章對「超級市場」嘅簡稱，而香港用先過大陸。報章標題縮短用語好多時都係為咗方便排版，呢個情況好常見，而「超市」用喺內文嘅情況喺香港舊報紙見唔到。香港大眾講「超市」其實係咪只係受到香港報章標題簡稱嘅影響呢？咁樣「超市」仲算唔算係「蝗語」呢？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">第二部分：「手機」／「手提電話」</span><br />\n<br />\n（1）「手提電話」喺香港舊報紙出現，最早可見於1986年。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/26/164726_12dede0fd4b9de4b9bba589d6cd9ce10.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F26%2F164726_12dede0fd4b9de4b9bba589d6cd9ce10.jpg&h=34cfafa7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖七：華僑日報，1986年6月28日。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/26/164809_fb9b9c390b06f53925011ca122e0f7e1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F26%2F164809_fb9b9c390b06f53925011ca122e0f7e1.jpg&h=b011f84b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖八：大公報，1987年3月17日。<br />\n<br />\n（2）「手機」喺香港舊報紙出現，最早可見於1995年。（1992-1994年間舊報紙比較難檢索到，改為搵期刊，但都係見唔到有「手機」）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/26/172702_c5d3658b3891384a4ec74104516ea985.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F26%2F172702_c5d3658b3891384a4ec74104516ea985.jpg&h=9055c696&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖九：文匯報，1995年4月13日。<br />\n<br />\n（3）「手機」喺《人民日報》出現，最早可見於1993年。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/26/165206_e483051164288e540e67a7a85f314398.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F26%2F165206_e483051164288e540e67a7a85f314398.jpg&h=9af9fbb1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖十：人民日報，1993年4月8日第7版。<br />\n<br />\n小結：香港舊報紙用「手機」一詞，遲過《人民日報》，而且係由《文匯報》、《大公報》帶頭用先，好可能係受到大陸影響，因此「手機」應該係「蝗語」。<br />\n<br />\n不足之處：因為時間同能力關係，只能睇到幾份報紙，而且又睇唔到電影電視，冇法子知道口語上係咪都有同樣情況，如果大家搵到其他資料，歡迎補充。"},{"pid":"2be73b8da74c265588169d0f6861d2f2eae778d8","tid":717768,"uid":185953,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T09:51:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁有心機"},{"pid":"ad3a9aa771acd2289ef7fe0adaca9ee6063963ea","tid":717768,"uid":12432,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2be73b8da74c265588169d0f6861d2f2eae778d8","tid":717768,"uid":185953,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T09:51:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁有心機"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T10:02:03.000Z","msg":"認真post預咗冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fc8f4374d51e1496cab7ef609ad67b782630c1c","tid":717768,"uid":138388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T10:05:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ce8cd9de3bc9f257e849d1fed01687f0c82e483","tid":717768,"uid":185953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad3a9aa771acd2289ef7fe0adaca9ee6063963ea","tid":717768,"uid":12432,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2be73b8da74c265588169d0f6861d2f2eae778d8","tid":717768,"uid":185953,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T09:51:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁有心機"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T10:02:03.000Z","msg":"認真post預咗冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T10:33:09.000Z","msg":"幫你推下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef1b25dbc555951be61cdf057facfb6f45b9069f","tid":717768,"uid":1159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T11:00:16.000Z","msg":"其實mmis 係好好嘅工具<br />\n<br />\n其實支付都唔係蝗語<br />\n唔記得咗係188X 定192X已經有用"},{"pid":"14b314467d30b990a3bb872988412cda36d200b9","tid":717768,"uid":12432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef1b25dbc555951be61cdf057facfb6f45b9069f","tid":717768,"uid":1159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T11:00:16.000Z","msg":"其實mmis 係好好嘅工具<br />\n<br />\n其實支付都唔係蝗語<br />\n唔記得咗係188X 定192X已經有用"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T11:05:38.000Z","msg":"如果啲報紙再齊啲就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25ebfc1318e125d44d510877701abe8085901b1e","tid":717768,"uid":711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T09:15:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71df8294c4d72b4c25e0a7df5de46f2cc49b4700","tid":717768,"uid":44391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T09:34:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fb37b9f8d20c5ae6fa23f704bd48f52f95fdd298","tid":717768,"uid":172521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T09:34:41.000Z","msg":"推 好有心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc66e9f4044b278e9c201bbec404615ec6fce07a","tid":717768,"uid":12432,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T09:58:53.000Z","msg":"而家睇返其實我搞錯咗最後張圖o) <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/04/174823_362a4174e0d94e78aadadffd22b68f7c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F04%2F174823_362a4174e0d94e78aadadffd22b68f7c.jpg&h=59f41c3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「手機」最早出現係《人民日報》係1996年，遲過《文匯報》<br />\n但係我又搵到另一個證據<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/04/175444_cd818384ef3cdfa2cc74ef056250973d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F04%2F175444_cd818384ef3cdfa2cc74ef056250973d.jpg&h=066b56e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n取自《光明日報》1994年5月2日，早過《文匯報》用「手機」呢個詞語"},{"pid":"ec15ab2ac4f98708f841fdf9446301fc45dc9f9a","tid":717768,"uid":136773,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T13:43:39.000Z","msg":"&quot;手機&quot;一定係大陸傳落嚟，首先&quot;telephone&quot;&quot;電話&quot;嚟自和製漢語取代上海人譯GE德律風<br />\n1876年發明telephone <br />\n1877年引入日本譯做&quot;電話&quot; <br />\n1878年引入上海譯做德律風<br />\n1920年代和制漢語淘汰哂中式譯法 (Physics <del>格致</del>物理  logic <del>名學</del>邏輯)果類<br />\n電話一詞就咁用咗幾十年<br />\n<br />\n-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n1973年發明咗可以拎住周圍行GE&quot;電話&quot; Mobile phone<br />\n80~90年代頭 手提電話得2個功能..打同聽，市民對佢GE印象仲係一部可以周圍行GE&quot;電話&quot; <br />\n日本譯做&quot;携帯電話&quot; 香港譯做&quot;手提電話&quot; 初期電話巨大外形又有&quot;水壺&quot;&quot;大哥大&quot;咁GE花名 <br />\n中國最早1987年喺廣東開通TACS制式流動網絡 果陣叫做&quot;廣東移動電話局&quot;<br />\n即係直到1987年都係稱呼&quot;手提電話&quot;&quot;移動電話&quot;<br />\n直到1995年中國只有15個省有流動網絡 <br />\n比起第一代體積細幾倍GE電話 對比起由&quot;水壺&quot;年代已經用緊GE香港人，Mobile phone發明近20年大陸人第一次見到外型更似一部&quot;對講機&quot;多於&quot;電話&quot;的東西...搜尋百度百科會發現1995年愛立信電話經典款式係用&quot;對講機&quot;嚟形容，加上後來功能又多咗，所以大陸人先會叫&quot;手機&quot;<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JTomxwx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJTomxwx.png&h=bdf10558&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n90年代中電話價格已經好親民 所以&quot;手機&quot;呢個詞比幾億人流傳，90年代中先開始普及"},{"pid":"3f554533e8a489a2a4dc755e9adedc414910a0af","tid":717768,"uid":18245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T14:22:57.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"4ba1b470d9c0b114b32ff84b58ba00181fb59ba7","tid":717768,"uid":120772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T09:53:56.000Z","msg":"樓主好有心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可唔可以搵多啲例子 整個系列出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03aeacf436f376e9622530dca84bf3def41ea93e","tid":717768,"uid":5150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T11:25:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> physics譯格致咁Chem譯做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f22fc275bdec569eaee2c7e674ade4f31e45750","tid":717768,"uid":71210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T13:31:55.000Z","msg":"支持樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f8a0c2232e9de961b07eb38118c2cf9265279a9","tid":717768,"uid":131441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T06:41:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"00382f112c5f1f19f8e639bf8c0d60a93a53e39f","tid":717768,"uid":10604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T07:04:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40cb5f79bd2cf11e0aa5274313aa53dc52c1fecb","tid":717768,"uid":83,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T15:49:13.000Z","msg":"LM一定要推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"625018d30725bbc0e6e88474273eac843180a9b6","tid":717768,"uid":10833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T04:06:45.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}